	quest.5BAD6277AAAA0001.quest_desc: [
		"&f&lThe Unearthed Truth &7- Reshiram is the truth of the original dragon. To claim its stone, witness the ancient past made flesh."
		""
		"&7Catch all 10 Ancient Paradox Pokemon:"
		"  &8- Great Tusk, Brute Bonnet, Flutter Mane, Scream Tail, Slither Wing"
