	quest.5BAD6477AAAA0001.quest_desc: [
		"&b&lThrough the Wormhole &7- Necrozma hungers for the light of Ultra Space. Hunt down every Ultra Beast that has crossed into this world."
		""
		"&7Catch every obtainable Ultra Beast:"
		"  &8- Blacephalon, Buzzwole, Guzzlord, Kartana, Naganadel"
