	quest.5BAD6577AAAA0001.quest_desc: [
		"&3&lThe Original Dragon &7- Kyurem is the empty husk of the dragon that Reshiram and Zekrom broke away from. Feed it the whole fractured timeline to make the husk whole again."
		""
		"&7Submit every obtainable Paradox Pokemon - all 10 Ancient and all 7 Future."
		""
		"&cThe submitted Paradox Pokemon will be consumed."
		""
		"&aReward: &fDNA Splicer&a - carry it to find &3Kyurem&a in frozen biomes, then make your own dna splicers to fuse Black or White Kyurem."
	]
