	quest.5BAD6877AAAA0001.quest_desc: [
		"&8&lThe Shadow's Brood &7- Marshadow is the smallest of legendaries, a shadow that slips into the spaces between. To call it from hiding, gather every Pokemon still young enough to fit in those spaces."
